  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, El Montasser et al. (2022) showed that CC market efficiency is largely affected by COVID-19. Al-Yahyaee et al. (2020) investigate the multifractality, long-memory process, and efficiency hypotheses of six major CCs (Bitcoin, Ethereum, Monero, Dash, Litecoin, and Ripple) using the time-rolling MF-DFA approach.",
    "They used a quantile regression approach to examine the determinants of the efficiency of these markets.",
    "Specifically, they support the significant impacts of volatility and liquidity as potential determinants of CC market efficiency.",
    "We collected the daily closing prices of the two largest CCs by market capitalization, Bitcoin and Ethereum, from https:// coinm arket cap. com.",
    "The sample period is from 08/07/2016 to 02/15/2023, yielding 2384 daily observations for each CC."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Similarly, El Montasser et al. (2022) showed that CC market efficiency is largely affected by COVID-19. Al-Yahyaee et al. (2020) investigate the multifractality, long-memory process, and efficiency hypotheses of six major CCs (Bitcoin, Ethereum, Monero, Dash, Litecoin, and Ripple) using the time-rolling MF-DFA approach."
  ]
